N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 403.3 - Designation of arbitrators by principals

State Regulations

Principals may redesignate arbitrators which have been
designated pursuant to section
185
(2)(a)
of the Navigation Law at any time
prior to the convening of a specific board of arbitration by filing written
notice upon the administrator. Notes
